\pard\f0\fs28 Variously associated with Sect.{\i  Macranthae} and Sect.{\i  Fruticulosae}; it resembles small plants of {\b 110} ({\i S. elegans} Link ex Brot.), but differs in the papillose leaves and in the tuberculate seeds.
